elements.text: What is Ujjivan Missed Call Banking?

text:
Ujjivan Missed Call Banking enables a customer to know his/her balance and mini statement by giving a missed call.


For

balance enquiry,

give a missed call on

9243012121



For

mini statement,

give a missed call on

9243032121

elements.text: How will I use Ujjivan Missed Call Banking if I have more than one account?

text: If you have more than one account with the Bank, pleaseuseUjjivan SMS Banking.
